html:
Like a female daemon
From another dimension
I came here unnoticed
To grin at you and blaze
I came with friends
One has eyes on antennas
Watches you with
All of his misery
Everything is on fire
But you cannot feel
A single flame
And the air is chill
The whispers are grim
But not worth a penny
Stars explodes in Andromeda
Weâ€™ll never know about it
title: Female daemon
